    <item>
      <title>日本股市因科技股抛售和美国经济衰退担忧而暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/japanese-stock-futures-slide-amid-concerns-over-us-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国制造业数据不佳，重新引发人们对美国经济衰退的担忧，日本股市遭遇一个月前进入熊市以来的最大跌幅，而全球科技股的抛售和日元走强也打压了市场人气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/japanese-stock-futures-slide-amid-concerns-over-us-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 23:41:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
